&lt;p&gt;We are a dynamic and innovative level 2 local neonatal unit. The unit has 28 cots with an additional 6 cots allocated to Transitional Care. The unit currently is working towards the Bliss Baby Charter accreditation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a Band 5 Nurse with an interest in Neonatal care or a nurse holding a recognised Neonatal qualification? If you are, we are looking for an enthusiastic individual to participate as a member of the neonatal multi-disciplinary team providing evidence based family centered care. The post holder will participate in assessing, implementation and evaluation of care for a designated group of babies and their parents. The post holder will require effective communication skills and to work as a member of the multidisciplinary team. The post holder will participate in his or her own professional development and will participate in the department internal rotational duties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a fixed term post, for 1 year covering a secondment.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Internal Candidates - please be aware, if you will make application the Internal Transfer Scheme will apply. For more details regarding this please contact Cody Izzard - 01438 286527&lt;/p&gt;
